  "updated_summary": "The Man in Orange Beanie, dressed in a brown long-sleeve shirt and an orange beanie, concluded a segment from behind a wooden table in a dimly lit home studio, stating, \"share them. So, I'll see you in the next one. Bye everyone.\" A blue bottle with a stylized logo, a professional microphone on a boom arm, and a large silver softbox light were positioned on the table, with a dark wall, circular mirror, framed picture, and couch forming the background. Following his farewell, thudding sounds and a click were audible as the Man in Orange Beanie looked at the camera, bent forward, and then detached the microphone from its boom arm, holding it while saying, \"Okay.\" He gestured with the microphone before stepping back to his right, still holding the equipment, and the scene concluded with a cut to black."
